OL,3,CUnions set out alternative plan for
OL,4,CTata Steel's site in Port Talbot
OL,5,Caimed at saving jobs
OL,7,FUnions have given Tata an alternative
OL,8,Fplan aimed at saving jobs at the
OL,9,Fbiggest steel plant in the country.
OL,11,FTata wants to decarbonise its site at
OL,12,FPort Talbot under moves to safeguard
OL,13,Fits future. Unions fear the plan
OL,14,Fwould lead to around 3,000 job losses.
OL,16,FThey have used independent
OL,17,Fconsultancy Syndex to draw up an
OL,18,Falternative plan for the site which
OL,19,Fwas presented to Tata on Friday 17
OL,20,FNovember.
